Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:57.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:59.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:04.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:07.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:14.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}狂った時計　刻む命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:18.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こぼれてく記憶の砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:22.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}芽生えた想いまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:27.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ねえ　こんなに呆気なく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:34.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消えてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:35.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish I was there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:38.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:44.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度となにも失くさぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:51.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}私を忘れて　始めて　Restart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:53.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:55.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:24:00.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:05.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.75,0:24:09.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For now I'll see you off
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:12.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:14.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.89,0:24:16.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:20.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.52,0:24:22.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:23.81,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:57.06,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:59.31,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的触碰 我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:04.82,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不 请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:07.19,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}尽管这绝望 不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:14.53,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}失准的时钟 记录着生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:18.54,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}散落满地的记忆之砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:22.33,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}以及萌生的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:27.46,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你看 却是那么轻易
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:34.76,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消失殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:35.85,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我希望能与你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:38.06,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.06,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的触碰 我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:44.44,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了不再失去曾经拥有的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:51.45,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让我忘却自己的过去 重新开始旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:53.66,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不 请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:55.58,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}尽管这绝望 不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:24:00.21,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}愿那让你苦不堪言的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:05.54,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}会迎来完结的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.75,0:24:09.34,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而我却要目送你离开
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:12.63,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:14.76,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.89,0:24:16.64,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:20.48,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.52,0:24:22.56,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:23.81,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你携手迈进
